filters: Model 2: OMNI solar wind dynamic pressure (Pdyn) only
sub_questions: What is the RMSE for Model 1 (Kp input)?
What is the RMSE for Model 2 (Pdyn input)?

format_notes: First 3 columns appear to be datetime components: year, day_of_year, hour
Fourth column is the measurement value
CDF file format requires special parsing tools

constraints: Only 23 hourly data points available for Kp and Pdyn
